│ *   **Security and Compliance:** Handling sensitive customer data requires robust security         │
│ measures. Implement encryption protocols and comply with data privacy and security regulations     │
│ like GDPR or CCPA.                                                                                 │
│ *   **Compatibility Issues:** Compatibility issues may arise if platforms don't follow the same    │
│ data formats or protocols.                                                                         │
│ *   **Lack of Real-Time Sync:** Some CRMs may only support scheduled or batch processes, not       │
│ real-time updates.                                                                                 │
