│ integration, performance benchmarks, and scalability planning.                                     │
│ *   **Map Business Processes:** Document your workflows clearly before starting any integration    │
│ development.                                                                                       │
│ *   **Prioritize Data Accuracy:** Ensure data accuracy by matching source fields precisely to CRM  │
│ fields, making required fields mandatory, and standardizing formats.                               │
│ *   **Secure API Implementation:** Use OAuth 2.0 for secure access, rotate API keys regularly, and │
